secutive years irving azoff called him the great hope for the music business and jimmy iovine commented that grainge is working to restore a spirit of risktaking and innovation by being willing and open to entrepreneurship and that kind of thing the record industry has gotten depleted of in an interview with grainge billboard wrote “if “power” means moving markets or greenlighting massive spends universal music group chairman lucian grainge demonstrated a staggering penchant for it when umg completed its  billion acquisition of emi’s recordedmusic assets in september  grainge is a fierce and tireless advocate for the recordedmusic business in  cnet wrote that “grainge is positioning universal to lead the pack” of major labels in their embracing of new digital opportunities a  frontpage la times profile of grainge said that if anyone can save the music business it might be grainge in  billboard wrote “in the age of spotify youtube and shazam grainge is positioned to tackle his business overriding priority win fair compensation for artists and take full ownership of content that other parties have been profiting from” contents  early life and career  universal music group  personal life  industry honours and other achievements  references  external links early life and careeredit lucian grainge grew up in north london grainge worked his way up in the london music scene after leaving queen elizabeths grammar school for boys at the age of  when he began working as a runner at a talent scout company called mpc after calling several record label heads from the music week directory he got through to maurice oberstein the chairman of cbc records who hired him for publishing company april musics ar department his first signing was the psychedelic furs in  he became the director of rca music publishing two years later he became an ar director for mca records he set up polygram music publishing in  and joined polydor as gm of ar and business affairs in  he was promoted to managing director of polydor in  and had success with acts including boyzone and the lighthouse family since becoming chairman and chief executive of universal music in  grainge has overseen a strategy to increase universals digital distribution international expansion and market leadership in both recorded music and publishing bestselling artists signed to universal music in recent years have included rihanna lady gaga jessie j amy winehouse carly rae jepsen and maroon  universal music groupedit grainge became the chairman of the uk division of the universal music group and later became chairman of universal music group international in  he served in this position until  on  january  he became ceo of the universal music group and later became chairman on  march  he succeeded doug morris who served as chairman and ceo since  grainge has been influential in universal music groups international digital expansion by pioneering distribution models with a wide range of technology partners including apple spotify bskyb rdio virgin media vodafone and  entertainment he recently established the licensed music service onestop china with baidu as well as a deal with bin to break taiwanese acts on the mainland there is also an agreement in place with reliance to start indias first mobile music service grainge also helped arrange the partnership between bravado universal musics entertainment merchandising division and tommy hilfiger and oversaw expansion for flagship classical labels deutsche grammophon and decca classics he also put together the global strategic partnership with entertainment company live nation within his first year as chairman  ceo of universal he led the company in acquiring emis recorded music operations in doing so he argued that selling to universal was the only way to make emi better and thus lift the entire industry he made the revitalisation of former emi labels such as capitol records and virgin records a key part of his strategy as a result of the emi acquisition grainge will go down as the master architect of what is likely to be the last big deal in the music business in the emi deal umg acquired the beatles catalogue umgs merchandising division bravado subsequently secured north american merchandising for the band umg is now creating a unified marketing strategy for the music and associated products of the most influential and beloved band in the history of music the wisdom of the acquisition was further illustrated by the quick success of the revitalized capitol music group in  capitol earned all the major grammy awards for the year with sam smith receiving best new artist record of the year and song of the year awards and beck winning album of the year in  grainge partnered with russell simmons brian robbins and steve rifkind to create all def music the first major labelaffiliated music company created specifically to sign develop and promote artists on youtube russell simmons called grainge the most innovative of music executives umg partnered with samsung in the spring of  to launch a music service in africa called the kleek featuring the companys international catalogue as well as local artists under grainges leadership umg has broken a string of records becoming the first company in the us to have nine of the top  songs on the digital charts according to soundscan and weeks later becoming the first company to hold all  of the top  spots on the billboard hot  chart according to an industry insider umgs enterprise value in  years stands to be closing in on  billion in  grainge was featured in a documentary film that depicts the life and death of late british singer amy winehouse entitled amy which was released theatrically in july in  vivendi announced that grainge agreed to extend his tenure as umg’s chairman and ceo until at least  stating he was key to its strategy under his leadership umg experienced growth in annual revenue digital recorded music revenue and ebitda personal lifeedit in january  grainge married his first wife attorney samantha berg that november she experienced complications while giving birth to their son elliot and fell into a coma from which she never recovered she died in england in  in  grainge married his second wife caroline their daughter alice was born in  in november  grainge and his wife reportedly paid  million usd for a house in pacific palisades they had previously leased a brentwood home from the owner of rhino entertainment his older brother was nigel grainge the founder of ensign records industry honours and other achievementsedit in  grainge was honoured with the prestigious music industry trusts’ award which recognises the world’s most influential and successful executives in music members of u presented him with the award and other acts he was associated with like take that performed grainge was appointed commander of the order of the british empire cbe in the  new year honours for services to the creative industries in  uk prime minister david cameron appointed him as a british business ambassador he was knighted in the  birthday honours for services to british business and inward investment he was inaugurated to appointment to the order of the british empire and knight bachelor by prince william on november   grainge is a trustee of the american friends of the royal foundation of the duke and duchess of cambridge and prince harry httpwwwroyalfoundationcomcontactus in  he received the humanitarian award from the foundation for ethnic understanding that same year umg was honoured with a sagaftra american scene award recognising the companys commitment to diversity as exemplified by its entire catalog and roster of artists in  he was awarded the presidents merit award icon award by the recording academy in recognition of his significant contributions to the music industry in  he will receive the spirit of life award from the city of hope recognizing his outstanding achievements in business and his dedication to philanthropic causes grainge serves on the boards of lionsgate and northeastern university in october  variety presented grainge with its  empowerment award for overseeing a noticeable shift in the demographics of the industry leader’s csuites” with women occupying some of the highest executive positions at universal music group in may  the cannes lions international festival of creativity announced that grainge would be honored as the  media person of the year he is the first music executive to be recognized since the award was launched in  he was awarded an honorary doctorate of music by the berklee college of music in may  and an honorary doctorate of global commerce by northeastern university in may of  referencesedit  debretts  the trusted source on british social skills etiquette and styledebretts debrettscom retrieved    pregrammy gala to honor lucian grainge grammycom   a b c lucian grainge the  billboard power  billboard   lucian grainge tops billboards  power  list fmqb   a b new boss for universal music lady gaga record label – time time  march    billboard reveals the  power  billboard   staff no  lucian grainge  power  billboard retrieved  august    a b c can this man save the music business los angeles times   billboard power  lucian grainge qa billboard   a b crank it up russell simmons universal music launch label – on youtube cnet   dead link  universal music group universalmusiccom retrieved    apple signs deal with universal music group for icloud major publishers also on board  billboard billboardbiz  retrieved    universal music group launching spotify playlist service for us fans  billboard billboardbiz  retrieved    dead link  universal music group universalmusiccom retrieved    universal music group universalmusiccom retrieved    dead link  dead link  baidu  investors  press releases irbaiducom  retrieved    indias reliance universal tie up for g music services the independent london  august    umgs bravado tommy hilfiger sign global branding deal  billboard b