 a coma from which she never recovered she died in england in  in  grainge married his second wife caroline their daughter alice was born in  in november  grainge and his wife reportedly paid  million usd for a house in pacific palisades they had previously leased a brentwood home from the owner of rhino entertainment his older brother was nigel grainge the founder of ensign records industry honours and other achievementsedit in  grainge was honoured with the prestigious music industry trusts’ award which recognises the world’s most influential and successful executives in music members of u presented him with the award and other acts he was associated with like take that performed grainge was appointed commander of the order of the british empire cbe in the  new year honours for services to the creative industries in  uk prime minister david cameron appointed him as a british business ambassador he was knighted in the  birthday honours for services to british business and inward investment he was inaugurated to appointment to the order of the british empire and knight bachelor by prince william on november   grainge is a trustee of the american friends of the royal foundation of the duke and duchess of cambridge and prince harry httpwwwroyalfoundationcomcontactus in  he received the humanitarian award from the foundation for ethnic understanding that same year umg was honoured with a sagaftra american scene award recognising the companys commitment to diversity as exemplified by its entire catalog and roster of artists in  he was awarded the presidents merit award icon award by the recording academy in recognition of his significant contributions to the music industry in  he will receive the spirit of life award from the city of hope recognizing his outstanding achievements in business and his dedication to philanthropic causes grainge serves on the boards of lionsgate and northeastern university in october  variety presented grainge with its  empowerment award for overseeing a noticeable shift in the demographics of the industry leader’s csuites” with women occupying some of the highest executive positions at universal music group in may  the cannes lions international festival of creativity announced that grainge would be honored as the  media person of the year he is the first music executive to be recognized since the award was launched in  he was awarded an honorary doctorate of music by the berklee college of music in may  and an honorary doctorate of global commerce by northeastern university in may of  referencesedit  debretts  the trusted source on british social skills etiquette and styledebretts debrettscom retrieved    pregrammy gala to honor lucian grainge grammycom   a b c lucian grainge the  billboard power  billboard   lucian grainge tops billboards  power  list fmqb   a b new boss for universal music lady gaga record label – time time  march    billboard reveals the  power  billboard   staff no  lucian grainge  power  billboard retrieved  august    a b c can this man save the music business los angeles times   billboard power  lucian grainge qa billboard   a b crank it up russell simmons universal music launch label – on youtube cnet   dead link  universal music group universalmusiccom retrieved    apple signs deal with universal music group for icloud major publishers also on board  billboard billboardbiz  retrieved    universal music group launching spotify playlist service for us fans  billboard billboardbiz  retrieved    dead link  universal music group universalmusiccom retrieved    universal music group universalmusiccom retrieved    dead link  dead link  baidu  investors  press releases irbaiducom  retrieved    indias reliance universal tie up for g music services the independent london  august    umgs bravado tommy hilfiger sign global branding deal  billboard billboardbiz  retrieved    universal music group universalmusiccom retrieved    emi publishing goes to sony label to universal  billboard billb