ber  universal music group’s lucian grainge serves as a champion of female leadership variety retrieved  october    sir lucian grainge named cannes lions media person of the year  canneslionscom retrieved  may    by  allen bush  rita moreno the isley brothers lucian grainge milton nascimento honored at commencement  berklee college of music berkleeedu retrieved    northeastern announces  honorary degree recipients news  northeastern retrieved  may   external linksedit the rise of lucian grainge mandelson web cutoff plan potentially illegal preceded by doug morris chairman  chief executive officer of universal music group  january  to present succeeded by incumbent retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleluciangraingeoldid categories living people birthsbritish businesspeopleamerican entertainment industry businesspeoplebritish music industry executivesamerican music industry executivesuniversal music groupcommanders of the order of the british empireknights bachelorpeople from pacific palisades los angeleshidden categories all articles with dead external linksarticles with dead external links from june pages containing london gazette template with parameter supp set to yengvarb from september use dmy dates from september articles with hcards navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version languages فارسیfrançais edit links this page was last edited on  july  at  text is available under the creative commons attributionsharealike license additional terms may apply by using this site you agree to the term